  "title": "SENIOR RESIDENT TECHNICAL OFFICERS (HDB BTO)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Carry out the supervision of BTO building works as stipulated in the Building Control Act</li>\n  <li>Ensure that proper processes and safe methods of construction are maintained by the main contractor</li>\n  <li>Co-ordinate and supervise the defects’ investigation and rectification Works</li>\n  <li>Organize and maintain proper site documentation and records</li>\n  <li>Able to perform Lead RTO role</li>\n  <li>Lead, manage and audit Supervision team</li>\n  <li>State expected salary</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>BCA-registered / NCCS / BCSS</li>\n  <li>Min 7 years’ experience in the supervision of C&amp;S/Architectural/M&amp;E works preferably in HDB BTO projects</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please send your resume to <u><strong>posts@jgp-group.com </strong></u>and indicate the position you are applying clearly.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted applicants will be notified</strong></em></p>",
